# ot

## What is it?

This package contains some usefull constants and funtions to deal with 
the [OpenTypeÂ® Specification](https://learn.microsoft.com/de-de/typography/opentype/spec/).

For details read the full [Documentation](https://fontstuff.gitlab.io/ot).

## How to use it?

```python
>>> from ot.table.name import getNameDescription
>>> getNameDescription(nameID=3)
'Unique Font Identifier'

>>> from ot.table.head import getMacStyleBitNames
>>> getMacStyleBitNames(3)
['Bold', 'Italic']
```
